"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Stock markets in Asia and Europe dropped because people are worried about a worldwide recession. Japan's main stock index, Topix, fell by 12%. European markets also went down at the start of trading on Monday. Cryptocurrencies also lost value. This happened after a big drop in global stock markets on Friday. Investors started buying more bonds because they wanted safer investments.\",            \"english_title\": \"Global Economic Concerns\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las bolsas de valores en Asia y Europa bajaron porque la gente est\u00e1 preocupada por una recesi\u00f3n mundial. El \u00edndice burs\u00e1til principal de Jap\u00f3n, Topix, cay\u00f3 un 12%. Los mercados europeos tambi\u00e9n bajaron al inicio de la jornada del lunes. Las criptomonedas tambi\u00e9n perdieron valor. Esto sucedi\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de una gran ca\u00edda en los mercados burs\u00e1tiles globales el viernes. Los inversores comenzaron a comprar m\u00e1s bonos porque quer\u00edan inversiones m\u00e1s seguras.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaciones Econ\u00f3micas Globales\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The government of Britain had an emergency meeting on Monday because there were riots by people who are against immigration. More than 150 people were arrested over the weekend. In Rotherham, criminals tried to set fire to a hotel where asylum-seekers live. In Middlesbrough, groups of far-right people fought with local Asians who were protecting their things. In many places, other people came out to protest against the anti-immigration groups.\",            \"english_title\": \"Political Unrest in Britain\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno de Gran Breta\u00f1a tuvo una reuni\u00f3n de emergencia el lunes porque hubo disturbios por personas que est\u00e1n en contra de la inmigraci\u00f3n. M\u00e1s de 150 personas fueron arrestadas durante el fin de semana. En Rotherham, criminales intentaron incendiar un hotel donde viven solicitantes de asilo. En Middlesbrough, grupos de personas de extrema derecha pelearon con asi\u00e1ticos locales que proteg\u00edan sus cosas. En muchos lugares, otras personas salieron a protestar contra los grupos antiinmigrantes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Inestabilidad Pol\u00edtica en Gran Breta\u00f1a\"        }    ]}"